r />\n<br />\n蕩娃黑鮑　帶來了吹水台<br />\n移花真貌　四格景致如畫<br />\nblog中叫怨　愚弄網民<br />\n扮病脫殼　無牽掛<br />\n<br />\n好一隻迎春鮑　誰人不愛它<br />\n好一隻迎春鮑　何來顏面對歌迷<br />\n我的野蠻一哥　可分發千張<br />\n睇多睇迎春鮑　人人齊共歡樂下"},{"pid":"5d746b1d1b5c6a9bf81f2f82e07f5f6b21b9bc17","tid":97703,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6ac4c999e920d3f8f2016d6b48ee566fec8ec7","tid":97703,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:25:56.000Z","msg":"你地真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a05c165b1b11c9e52783e0a6365808d7349643","tid":97703,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:27:24.000Z","msg":"令我想起黑色的鮑鮑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a98dbdad1f4d0117854e7b5e4c81d94b1d63432","tid":97703,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁就十年"},{"pid":"157cdbbb6a05a1fa68cde4e2f90981ad5555a519","tid":97703,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"圖？link?"},{"pid":"8f25a6dd3390af31dd563efe34af20039876e96e","tid":97703,"uid":42330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"又一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ae2f98718db88a7bc20f919edcded25e47b05e","tid":97703,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"年經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3257b56fd99106c0af10db0d17bea3a0d91dbe","tid":97703